turns.content: Cancer is a water sign and is known for its emotional and intuitive nature. People born under the sign of Cancer are generally nurturing, caring, and protective of those they love. They are also known for their strong memories and their ability to hold on to the past, both good and bad. Cancers tend to be sensitive and compassionate, and they are often described as being "motherly." They can also be moody and may have a tendency to retreat into their shell when feeling hurt or vulnerable. Overall, Cancer is a complex and deeply emotional sign that is known for its strong relationships and its love of home and family.
